OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA dry and
OL,6,Fwarm evening with late sunshine. Skies
OL,7,Fwill cloud over through the night with
OL,8,Fsome spells of rain in the early hours
OL,9,Fof the morning, particuarly in
OL,10,FCornwall.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSunday:FCloudy at first in the morning
OL,13,Fwith a few showery outbreaks of rain.
OL,14,FTurning drier through the day with
OL,15,Fincreasing amounts of sunshine.
OL,16,FFeeling much fresher than recent days.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
